{
  "stem": "1491.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then, they put us in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we didn't get one word of encouragement that we'll be alive, only temporary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In those barracks, they have your toiletry, the bowl of soup what they gave you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The bowl you used for your toilet and you used to eat your soup.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the hunger was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it was cold-- we had no clothes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And every morning, they count us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Always they were counting us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then I was pulled out from the line.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They called this appell where they're counting us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "A German came over and pulled me out, and pulled two or three people besides me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were sure this is our-- I would look at my mother, and I said this is-- we-- they pulled me to go to the ovens.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Meanwhile, they took me to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And because I didn't look too bad, like I told you, always that's my nature since the baby.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I've been always on the heavy side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And took me to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the doctor came over, and he was really kind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he says, don't worry, I won't hurt you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But we needs blood for the soldiers who are on the front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They are dying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we need blood transfusions for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That time, Jewish blood was good for them-- wasn't anymore rassenschande.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rassenschande, because they said we are a different race.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You cannot mix with Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that blood wasn't considered bad blood, because this was saving the wounded soldiers from the front.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took from me a bottle of-- like a bottle of milk, so much blood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says, you'll get extra portion of bread for it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
